title: Top.Story.Weekly.06.04.17.political.sketch.comedy.45m.H.264.mp4
description:
Almost every week for about 16 years, we've put out a political sketch comedy show at the iO West theater in Hollywood called Top Story! Weekly. Please enjoy the show!

Usually the show consists of a half hour of sketches, a stand up, a fake news segment like SNL's weekend update, and a desk piece like you'd see on a late night talk show. Actors and stand ups are drawn from the best of Hollywood's performers. 

The stand up will be redacted for online so come see the show live!

iO West Theater in Hollywood
6366 Hollywood Blvd

Sundays, 8pm
